2024-01-31 07:33:57 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Discuss\Post:Insert {"timestamp":1706686437,"user_id":null,"user_ip":"206.206.69.34","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (X11; Linux x86_64) AppleWebKit\/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\/103.0.0.0 Safari\/537.36 Vivaldi\/5.3.2679.68","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post","entity_data":{"id":9889,"__foreign_props":[],"parent_id":"0","cat_id":"1","project_id":"1579","nick":"Alex","topic":"quick question","content":"Hi, this is Alex with Offshore Wolf, I was just looking at the service section of your website and specifically thought of reaching out to you. \r\n\r\nWe provide full time virtual support to businesses like yours and with us you can hire a full time virtual assistant for just $99 a week. \r\n\r\nYou heard it right, a full time 40 hours a week virtual employee for just $99 a week. \r\n\r\nA full time 40 hour a week VA means you get a dedicated VA who works full time exclusively for you and your company without juggle between different clients. \r\n\r\nOur VAs are fluent in English, industry trained, and work side by side with your team on the timezone of your choice. \r\n\r\nNot just that, you can onboard our VAs as your own employee and communicate with our VA as you wish, whether that be on Slack, CRM or even smoke signals, how you wish to communicate, it's entirely upto you. \r\n\r\nYour team can interview our VAs, check their portfolios, and trial task them without paying a single dollar, meaning you'd only pay once our VAs actually start working for your company.\r\n\r\nOn top of everything, we are a US based company based meaning we accept all major credit\/debit cards.\r\n\r\nIf you're interested, please send a simple 'YES' and I'll wire one of our team members to speak with you.","create_date":"2024-01-31 07:33:57","modify_date":"2024-01-31 07:33:57","status":"published","is_moderated":0,"attachments":[],"_uid":2531631},"entity_changes":false}
